qMetaDef.title: Financial Performance Insight
qMetaDef.description: This sheet provides an overview of financial performance, with charts displaying trends in Accounts Receivable, Revenue, Amount Overdue by Customers, and Expenses, as well as breakdowns of Revenue and Expenses

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Revenue vs Last Year Revenue = '& num(Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(=vYTDYear)}, FiscalMonthNum={"<=$(vCurrentMonthNum)"}>}[Sales Price]*[Sales Quantity])/Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(=(vYTDYear)-1)}, FiscalMonthNum={"<=$(vCurrentMonthNum)"}>}[Sales Price]*[Sales Quantity]), '#,##0%')

qDef.qDef: (Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}>} AROpen)-Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}>} ARCurrent))/Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}>} AROpen)

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Account Receivable Overdue  =  ' & num((Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}>} AROpen)-Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}>} ARCurrent))/Sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}>} AROpen), '#,##0%')

qDef.qDef: ='Sales trend Current year America vs EMEA'
qDef.qLabelExpression: ='Sales trend Current year America vs EMEA'

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Expenses vs. Target  =  ' & num(sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}, _HistoryFlag={1}>} ExpenseActual)/sum({<[Fiscal Year]={$(vYTDYear)}, _HistoryFlag={1}>} ExpenseBudget), '#,##0%')
